PeerJS,provides,a,simple,peer,to,peer,data,sharing,API,that,functions,by,wrapping,WebRTC,It,provides,true,binary,data,support,and,can,preconnect,to,clients,for,faster,connection,establishment,Each,peer,wishing,to,share,data,simply,provides,an,identifier,that,other,peers,using,the,same,API,key,can,connect,to,The,PeerJS,service,deals,with,WebRTC,handshake,and,handles,NAT,traversals,for,the,users,PeerJS,brokers,connections,by,connecting,to,PeerServer,Users,can,choose,to,run,their,own,PeerServer,or,use,a,free,version,hosted,by,PeerJS,This,hosted,server,can,be,accessed,programmatically,via,JavaScript,API